title: #99: Scrappy Doo (Greg Fitzsimmons)
itunes:title: Scrappy Doo with Greg Fitzsimmons
description: Greg Fitzsimmons had me over to his garage to tell me how much he loves to fight. Not organized fights. Just fights. Just regular, two dudes don't know each other and then one is punching the other, fights. It's a pretty fun podcast. What he does in the car is hard for me to wrap my head around.
